{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 84885, "create_time": 1650718777, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "如果控制机器让它精准地完成按键操作，那它是不是会成为世界上最优秀的钢琴家？", "timestamp": 1650718777}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 84891, "create_time": 1650718891, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "那也得优秀的钢琴家/音乐家去指定各种强弱和速度的变化吧", "timestamp": 1650718891}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 84892, "create_time": 1650718973, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我觉得单独自动演奏的机械系统是不可能代替钢琴家的，顶多能完美复刻钢琴家们的表现；但如果有学会表演音乐的AI的话就另说了。我猜前者很简单而后者现在应该还没能发展到该程度？", "timestamp": 1650718973}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 84902, "create_time": 1650720025, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "这理论不和用百度翻译就行了，学英语干啥一样", "timestamp": 1650720025}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 84904, "create_time": 1650720166, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 问题就在于怎么判断演奏的好坏。对于钢琴家可能他们会根据自己灵感在轻重缓急上做些微调，继续就得有人教。但是，一般人肯定是达不到钢琴家的水准的，能弹得和原谱一样就很完美了，所以我觉得一般人学钢琴实在是太无聊了🙈", "timestamp": 1650720166}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 84905, "create_time": 1650720211, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 钢琴入门的时候当然就是”按下/不按下“，但实际上人手所做的，除了”按下/不按下“，还有按照什么样的方式发力按下、按照什么样的速度按下，一些方式比其他方式更好听。", "timestamp": 1650720211}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 84906, "create_time": 1650720213, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 翻译很可能会出错，机器你只要给它谱和